						               													<description>The King has chosen you to be the warrior who finally ends the bloody war that has been going on for years between the two strongest races that inhabit the lands of Lundor, the Elves and the Barbarians. After thousands of casualties on both sides, there is only one option left to end the war once and for all. THE FINAL DUEL. This fight to the death between the two best warriors of the two factions will determine who will be the victor and who will claim for himself the lands of Lundor. Since ancient times, the final duel has been used as a last resort and takes place in Rindel's castle. Which warrior will be the victor? The Barbarian or the Elf?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Super Castle Fighter is a card-based combat game for 1-2 players ages 12+ that plays in 15-30 minutes created by Victor Robles, designed by Lizuren Games and published by The Game Crafter. Each player chooses a character and must fight to the death using cards as special techniques. The player who wins 2 rounds by reducing the opponent's life to 0 is the winner. To use an attack card or special move, you must pay the cost with your controller cards. The opponent can counter those attacks by blocking or using instant cards on the opponent's turn. Some attacks require power points. Accumulate power and spend it at the right time to deal the final blow and claim victory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
